Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 3 I made a decision most people told me was dumb — I gave everything away for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.78,0:00:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.18,0:00:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}9 years in crypto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}AI's trading my thousand dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I had a choice that day — turn this into a paid product, or make it a public experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I picked the expensive one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}13 lessons, free.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.51,0:00:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Live balance, free.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Every trade, every win rate, every drawdown — free.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The only thing behind the paywall — the specific parameters that would let a copycat clone the strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A friend asked me — you're burning your own bridge, you know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I told him no.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This is the only honest promise I can make.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Because if I'm wrong, I want everyone to watch me be wrong in real time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And if I'm right, same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Want people to trust what you're building?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Let them watch it work for free, first.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:01:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 4 tomorrow — the bug I almost didn't check.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.89,0:01:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Follow along.
